  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514190/extras/780427cc67d3ed3b13315a4a7145d522.poster.avif?t=1660918714\" width=616 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514190/extras/780427cc67d3ed3b13315a4a7145d522.webm?t=1660918714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514190/extras/780427cc67d3ed3b13315a4a7145d522.mp4?t=1660918714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>First, the Mayor of the city hanged himself. <br>Then the endless rain started.<br>And now someone knocking on my door. Who could it be? <br><br>You are in a noir adventure game where you will play a cat detective who needs to investigate the suicide of the Mayor of Sunny city. Suddenly the rain started to drop endlessly and no one knows why.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514190/extras/779f1868ed1144e440d0cdc697060f92.poster.avif?t=1660918714\" width=620 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514190/extras/779f1868ed1144e440d0cdc697060f92.webm?t=1660918714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514190/extras/779f1868ed1144e440d0cdc697060f92.mp4?t=1660918714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>So you are in the game now and will have to find a killer by:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Combining pieces of evidence<br></li><li>Resolving puzzles<br></li><li>Talking to people<br></li><li>Resolving detective mystery</li></ul><br>Hope you'll like the adventure. Step in!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514190/extras/780427cc67d3ed3b13315a4a7145d522.poster.avif?t=1660918714\" width=616 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514190/extras/780427cc67d3ed3b13315a4a7145d522.webm?t=1660918714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514190/extras/780427cc67d3ed3b13315a4a7145d522.mp4?t=1660918714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>First, the Mayor of the city hanged himself. <br>Then the endless rain started.<br>And now someone knocking on my door. Who could it be? <br><br>You are in a noir adventure game where you will play a cat detective who needs to investigate the suicide of the Mayor of Sunny city. Suddenly the rain started to drop endlessly and no one knows why.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514190/extras/779f1868ed1144e440d0cdc697060f92.poster.avif?t=1660918714\" width=620 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514190/extras/779f1868ed1144e440d0cdc697060f92.webm?t=1660918714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514190/extras/779f1868ed1144e440d0cdc697060f92.mp4?t=1660918714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>So you are in the game now and will have to find a killer by:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Combining pieces of evidence<br></li><li>Resolving puzzles<br></li><li>Talking to people<br></li><li>Resolving detective mystery</li></ul><br>Hope you'll like the adventure. Step in!",
